OL,3,C'Serious incident' leaves horse trials
OL,4,Cabandoned
OL,6,FA 'serious incident' at the Penrith
OL,7,Fhorse trials has led to the event
OL,8,Fbeing cancelled.
OL,10,FBritish Eventing Official have written
OL,11,Fon social media saying "Due to a
OL,12,Fserious incident that took place this
OL,13,Fafternoon, all competition at Penrith
OL,14,Fon 18 and 19 July has been abandoned."
OL,16,FThe competition was due to take place
OL,17,Fthis weekend at Frenchfield Farm in
OL,18,FPenrith, and is run by the Northern
OL,19,FCounties Horse Trials (NCHT).
